This directory contains custom ebuilds made by Jonathan Hunt 
<jhuntnz@users.sourceforge.net>. These ebuilds are for the Gentoo
Linux (http://www.gentoo.org) Portage tree. To use them checkout
the portage dir and add it to the PORTDIR_OVERLAY in /etc/make.conf.

To checkout the portage dir follow the instructions at 
http://sourceforge.net/cvs/?group_id=61715
The module you need to checkout is portage.
